# Layer A content lives here.
#
# Drop one curated markdown file per role/venture, matching the schema in
# ../config.ts. Each file is a REVIEWED copy-over of a vault `career-role`
# note — only the accomplishments cleared for publication, no PII, no
# un-consented employer identity (ADR-019 invariant 4), every claim tracing
# to a real note (invariant 3).
#
# This collection is intentionally empty until the `/career-interview` intake
# produces real role notes. While empty, Layer A renders an honest
# "intake in progress" state rather than placeholder accomplishments.
#
# Example file (src/content/roles/example-role.md.txt is shipped as a
# reference shape — note the .txt suffix keeps it OUT of the build):
